{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2a86f9c69","title":"关于改变庐山会议人员分组办法的建议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2b53b817aa","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":16,"articleId":"a2a86f9c69"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"14429badcd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时正在庐山举行的中共中央政治局扩大会议。尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cdc97d9931","type":"title","text":"关于改变庐山会议！人员分组办法的建议","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69"},{"id":"14429badcd","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、恩来、尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69"},{"id":"14dee2f850","type":"paragraph","text":"建议北京来的同志参加各大区小组的，即日改换一下，例如：参加华东小组的，改为参加中南、华南联合小组或他区，参加西北小组的改为参加华东或他处，如此类推。今日立即排出一个新表，明日起，照新表办事。这样做，见闻将广博多了，可能大有益处。至于各区省委书记，是否也应有一部分人（例如一半或三分之一）也照此样，改入他区，以广见闻，请你们药定，我无定见。是否由你们找各大区区长及中央少数同志，座谈一下，以利决定？谈一个钟头就够了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69"},{"id":"6ee68cb73a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69"},{"id":"bde83e531a","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十六日上午六时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69"}],"page":{"id":"67ea41b29d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"a2a86f9c69","start":189,"end":189}}}},"__N_SSG":true}